A%BFn/Qu%E1%BA%B7c-ng%C6%B0/poem-BDw_JfiYtX1JljsxogXtUg">Quặc ngư - 攫魚</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Vu-V%C5%A9-L%C4%83ng/T%E1%BA%A3o-xu%C3%A2n-s%C6%A1n-h%C3%A0nh/poem-pxd9F0nwLhpXr-RGSHZ_ew">Tảo xuân sơn hành - 早春山行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Vu-V%C5%A9-L%C4%83ng/author-9OdB40-NegtUYsATvAJH4Q">Vu Vũ Lăng</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-%C4%91o%E1%BA%A3n-c%C3%BA-ng%C3%A2m/poem-0vGlfCzjqWHY9ygox9A2fw">Trường đoản cú ngâm - 長短句吟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/author-14GcnhLjD2ajP0MTgtX13Q">Ngô Thì Nhậm</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
